These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-4-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: purple, blood-red, black, fuchsia, lilac, ivory, coral
The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker, electrician, lawyer, mechanic, police-officer, scientist
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, climbing, cricket, cycling, lacrosse, skateboarding, snowboarding
7 different pets are kept: frog, chinchilla, rabbit, goldfish, snake, mouse, hedgehog
 1. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the mechanic is the owner of the mouse##1
 4. the person who likes purple is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the owner of the frog is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who likes ivory##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the accountant##3
 8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
10. the scientist is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
11. the police-officer is the person who likes black##1
12. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
13. the mechanic is on the right of the dressmaker##1
14. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who likes black##1
15. the person who likes black is between the accountant and the owner of the snake##2
16. the police-officer is on the left of the electrician##1
17. the person who likes fuchsia is the owner of the snake##1
18. the lawyer is on the far left or far right##3
19. the police-officer is on the left or right of the accountant##3
20. the police-officer is the person who likes black##1
21. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
22. the person who likes coral is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
23. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the accountant##3
24. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left or far right##3
25. the mechanic is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
26. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |       3        |       4       |     5      |     6      |      7       |
| Color        | blood-red | ivory     | black           | fuchsia          | lilac  | coral | purple         |
| Job         | scientist  | accountant | police-officer | electrician   | dressmaker | mechanic   | lawyer       |
| Sport       | lacrosse   | badminton  | cricket        | skateboarding | climbing   | cycling    | snowboarding |
| Pet   | hedgehog        | goldfish       | frog           | snake         | rabbit     | mouse       | chinchilla    |

