12. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
13. the owner of the snake is in the middle##1
14. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
15. the owner of the goat is on the left of the teacher##1
16. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the turkish##3
17. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
18. the doctor is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
19. the doctor is on the left of the australian##1
20. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
